1 big box of lime Jello
1 big can of pears
1 8oz package of cream cheese
1 large container of cool whip

Boil juice from pears (2 cups, or add water to get to 2 cups).  
Add jello.  Put in refrigerator till semi-stiff.  
In blender, put pears & cream cheese, and add Jello and run it until well combined/mixed.
Put in a 9x13 pan and fold in cool whip.  
Put in refrigerator until firm.
